column67: MAKE A REGRET PER KILOMETER GRAPH

column31: As suburb size grows we see that for all bus stop sizes, we increase our regret to extra buses ratio at a similar rate.

Overall, using less bus stops will result in us having a slightly higher ratio of regret to the number of buses used. This could be caused by the fact that we use many more buses in a larger system for the ZRM so this offsets the steady increase in regret
